text: Unbreakable is the eleventh studio album by the American singer, Janet Jackson. It was released on October 2, 2015. As of September 2015, two R&B; tinged singles had been released from the album. One was "No Sleeep" which features American rapper J-Cole. The other was the title track. This will be Jackson's first album with newly recorded material since 2008's "Discipline". ==Track listing== ==Release history== Region Date Format Label Ref.
